that will help us heal.

02:05.325 --> 02:10.630 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: Public Health
Director Trudy Raymundo was at
the holiday lunch where Syed
Farook

02:10.630 --> 02:16.803 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
