practice, but it's not clear who
led the way to violence.

02:34.221 --> 02:37.224 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
DAVID BOWDICH, FBI Assistant
Director: We have learned and
believe that both subjects

02:37.224 --> 02:41.395 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
