direct link to the attack.

03:01.515 --> 03:03.183 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
BARACK OBAMA, President of the
United States: The threat from
terrorism is real, but we

03:03.183 --> 03:05.452 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
