reassure the nation.

03:10.724 --> 03:16.530 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
BARACK OBAMA: Our success won't
depend on tough talk or
abandoning our values or giving

03:16.530 --> 03:22.135 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
