second and final week of the
U.N. conference.

04:58.565 --> 05:02.402 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
U.N. Secretary-General Ban
Ki-Moon warned ministers from
nearly 200 countries not to

05:02.402 --> 05:05.972 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
