results will challenge years of
Socialist domination in the
Latin

06:03.163 --> 06:05.298 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
America oil state.

06:05.298 --> 06:09.836 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
