it: Opposition candidates won 99
seats to the ruling Socialist

06:46.306 --> 07:05.425 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Party's 46, with 22 races
still outstanding.

07:05.425 --> 07:10.430 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
