ground, and we have to fight
them

28:56.468 --> 28:58.904 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
on the Internet.

28:58.904 --> 29:01.239 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
SEN. TED CRUZ (R-TX),
Presidential Candidate: We don't
need a president who goes on
national

29:01.239 --> 29:06.945 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
television and lectures the
American people like a
schoolmarm, that condescends to
the

29:06.945 --> 29:11.450 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
