29:17.222 --> 29:18.957 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
SEN. MARCO RUBIO (R-FL),
Presidential Candidate: And
people are scared not just
because of

29:18.957 --> 29:20.826 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
these attacks, but because of a
growing sense that we have a
president that is completely

29:20.826 --> 29:23.228 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
overwhelmed by them.

29:23.228 --> 29:27.232 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I'm very disappointed tonight. I
think not only did the president
not make things better

29:27.232 --> 29:31.236 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
tonight. I fear he may have made
things worse in the minds of
many Americans.

29:31.236 --> 29:34.339 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SEN. LINDSEY GRAHAM (R-SC),
Presidential Candidate: The
president is misleading us about
the 65-nation

29:34.339 --> 29:39.378 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
coalition. It's only on paper.
There is no answer, other than
destroying ISIL. The president

29:39.378 --> 29:41.747 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
