to be abroad.

30:04.703 --> 30:06.872 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
AMY WALTER, The Cook Political
Report: Where do we even begin?

30:06.872 --> 30:08.774 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: Where to begin.

30:08.774 --> 30:13.578 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
AMY WALTER: We just -- for a guy
