30:46.445 --> 30:50.982 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: As we speak, there
have been denunciations from Jeb
Bush, who called him unhinged,
from

30:50.982 --> 30:54.786 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Lindsey Graham, from other
Republican candidates. Ted Cruz
has said, "That's not my
position."

30:54.786 --> 30:56.321 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
That's all he said.

30:56.321 --> 30:59.024 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
