30:59.024 --> 31:04.496 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
TAMARA KEITH, National Public
Radio: She did. She tweeted and
said that this doesn't make

31:04.496 --> 31:09.067 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
