said this is not the right thing
to be saying.

31:34.126 --> 31:37.729 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
That said, Donald Trump is
getting the ratings he wants.
People are talking about him.

31:37.729 --> 31:38.130 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
GWEN IFILL: Here we are.

31:38.130 --> 31:39.164 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
