rein given to a non-government
environmental group.

37:47.599 --> 37:53.371 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Fred de Sam Lazaro reports from
China as a part of his ongoing
series Agents for Change.

37:53.371 --> 37:59.811 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
FRED DE SAM LAZARO: The
inspectors came calling recently
at this massive textile factory
in

37:59.811 --> 38:05.517 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
