year for clothing makers and
retailers around the world.

38:19.898 --> 38:25.770 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
This plant also produces some
60,000 tons of waste water, and
a 2013 investigation found

38:25.770 --> 38:29.440 align:left position:25%,start line:86.67% size:75%
