adequately treated.

38:29.440 --> 38:34.546 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Manager Wang Wei said millions
of dollars were invested to
upgrade the system.

38:34.546 --> 38:40.552 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WANG WEI, Vice President,
Saintyear (through translator):
Today, we invited IPE in to show

38:40.552 --> 38:44.656 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
them our changes, our
improvement in environmental
protection, so their inspectors
can see we

38:44.656 --> 38:47.158 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
