government requirements.

38:47.158 --> 38:53.031 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
FRED DE SAM LAZARO: But IPE, the
inspectors, are not from the
all-powerful government.

38:53.031 --> 39:00.605 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The Institute of Public and
Environmental Affairs, is a
small non-government
organization.

39:00.605 --> 39:09.013 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
IPE founder Ma Jun has won
international awards for his
environmental activism, with no
apparent

39:09.013 --> 39:14.953 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
objection from the government.
