Linda Greer of the
Washington-based NRDC, the
Natural

39:20.024 --> 39:23.661 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Resources Defense Council,
which has partnered with IPE.

39:23.661 --> 39:27.298 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
LINDA GREER, Natural Resources
Defense Council: I think he's an
astute observer of what are

39:27.298 --> 39:31.769 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
the problems and how can they
best be solved in China.

39:31.769 --> 39:36.674 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
FRED DE SAM LAZARO: Ma was an
investigative journalist in the
1990s, when he began documenting

39:36.674 --> 39:40.645 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
