39:40.645 --> 39:46.351 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MA JUN, Founder, Institute of
Public and Environmental
Affairs: Like in those cancer
village, a group

39:46.351 --> 39:55.560 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
